title: Openstreetmap, Cyprus Points of Interest, Cyprus, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Cyprus Points of Interest, Cyprus, 2008
description: This data was provided by the people over at Open street maps, and shows various points of interest throughout Cyprus. This point level data is divided by feature type, which includes restaurants, places of worship, fuel, parking, and various other points. The Data also has a name attribute which gives more specific details for the location.
